{"tid":1756411,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"J19藍田選區需要大家幫忙！！！","createTime":"2019-11-26T04:28:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T11:55:45.000Z","uid":70580,"like":86,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":123,"replies":[{"pid":"5123e6c4ed03e8e914c141f9116c8da80beb386d","tid":1756411,"uid":70580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"尋日我係票站裡面30個鐘！<br />\n除左票站主任極度on9之外，<br />\n無端端有個律師同一個所謂保安定唔知義工出現左，<br />\n戴住個證，但sip埋係西裝袋，<br />\n問佢係邊個，佢又唔肯show證.....<br />\n唔肯講佢自己係邊個。<br />\n係居民起哄既時候，仲話「警察唔該！」企圖叫警察驅散我地，恐嚇我地既居民。<br />\n最後重要走後門咁走左...........<br />\n我地而家想搵返個個人係邊個....<br />\n皆因佢淨係比左一個名我....<br />\nAlbert Poon <br />\n只要prove到佢係唔知邊個但允許入票站，咁就可以嘗試更有力地做選舉呈請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫下森仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好當佢condom... 無手足係condom...<br />\n真係好想本土入到議會啊.....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UiU84Dm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUiU84Dm.jpg&h=e08983f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f35193e29c4d339e23991d71205187952fbd4fc","tid":1756411,"uid":91438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:30:18.000Z","msg":"藍田友推"},{"pid":"c1389e1933e2b6992402320706a96aaada1b36f1","tid":1756411,"uid":22921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:30:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"56515f2a33968831a0020c0d97ddf621f56b6807","tid":1756411,"uid":33437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:31:29.000Z","msg":"pushq"},{"pid":"6df737c25ed829e6e601d0056c91717073cf09d5","tid":1756411,"uid":205909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:31:35.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"89c8c5b3fce9354cd6ad439009e3768192769d11","tid":1756411,"uid":285324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:32:43.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆街保皇黨，一度都嫌多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e5b00753d6a7739f70535b2cdc073a2657767b3","tid":1756411,"uid":267277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:33:54.000Z","msg":"#區選 #藍田 #飛雁幼稚園<br />\n<br />\n1446 2號候選人馮德森表示問題選票多達70張或以上 而2號候選人與1號候選人工聯會簡鉻東勝出選票只相差50張 馮曾要求票站主任重新點票 但遭票站主任拒絕 馮將考慮選舉呈請"},{"pid":"e08a9b282582a06305b70e3a903086dbfb318efc","tid":1756411,"uid":160795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:33:57.000Z","msg":"大家好！想同大家介紹一個新 Channel- FundHKers<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKersFund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKersFund&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV05IBJzpNVIoVNH6FP0f0bDA%3D&h=1d2ce67b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKersFund</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家平時捐錢捐開邊到？<br />\n星火？立場？<br />\n但其實香港仲有好多機構要大家支持！Channel入面會不定期Share唔同類型嘅機構同眾籌比大家課金。<br />\n<br />\nAdmin會Factcheck眾籌嘅可信程度，認為可信同有急切性先會推比大家！<br />\n<br />\n當然捐唔捐 捐幾多 由自己選擇<br />\n就算能力所限都可以Share比身邊朋友。總之一句到尾，香港人撐香港人！"},{"pid":"670debf091ccab1be52861c976a035caaef950d4","tid":1756411,"uid":267277,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:34:59.000Z","msg":"森仔真係好比心機做左好多野<br />\n全部街坊都看在眼裡"},{"pid":"b193dca0040a10b683ab029b254a3c60ac07dce5","tid":1756411,"uid":335894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T04:35:29.000Z","msg":"推啊!<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" c